      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "I understand how you feel, but remember, you are not a burden. Your life has meaning and value, even if it feels like it's fading. It's okay to feel like you're waiting for the lights to go out, but it's not the end. There are still moments of beauty and joy to be found, even in the darkest times. You don't have to wait for the lights to go out. You can choose to keep going, even if it's just for a little while longer.",
      "source": "target",
